\id 2PE - Kalam NT [kmh] -Papua New Guinea 1992 (DBL 2014) 
\h 2 Piyta 
\toc1 Piyta Minj Kisen Tikak 
\toc2 2 Piyta 
\toc3 2 Piyt 
\mt1 2 PIYTA  
\mt2 Piyta Minj Kisen Tikak  
\imt1 Minim Nind Niŋep  
\ip Piyta minj kisen tikak biy aŋgak, “Nimb Gor ker mindpim gok, aŋgip rek giy mindrep ginimimb. Pen Gor aŋgip rek aspun aŋgiy, minim yesek apay ak ma dinimimb; Jiysis Krays minim niŋind yimb aŋgñinuk anep direp giy, andkind winiŋgamb ñin ak kond mindenimimb aŋgak.”  
\iot Minim Ar Keykey Mindip Rek:  
\io1 Minim nind aŋgak ak mindip, chapta 1:1-2.  
\io1 Gor ker mindpim rek, mindrep ginimimb aŋgak minim ak mindip, chapta 1:3-21.  
\io1 Biynimb Gor minim yesek apay gok, minim kuyip ak ma niŋnimimb aŋgak minim ak mindip, chapta 2:1-22.  
\io1 Jiysis kisen andkind winiŋgamb aŋgak minim ak mindip, chapta 3:1-18.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Yand Saymon Piyta, Jiysis Krays nup woŋg giy, minim nup dand tapiyn. Minj tiksipiyn kun biy, nimbip biynimb Jiysis Krays Gor suŋ-tep chin ak gos tep ñiyiŋg, biynimb di Nop yip jimñiy ayip ak niŋiy, nup chiŋgem, jimñiy tep gakniŋ mindpun gok tiksipiyn.  
\v 2 Nimb Biyomb chin Gor apiymiŋay kuyip gosimb niŋmindem, nimbip kond minder, mindrep giniŋgambim.   
\s1 Gor Nuk Key Chinup Niŋay Dak Ak, Nup Chiŋgrep Ginjun  
\p
\v 3 Gor Biyomb tep yimb ak, biynimb yand mindeyaŋ aŋgiy, chinup niŋayak ak mey; nup gosimb niŋbun. Kun ak mindrep giniŋg nup chiŋgrep giy, tap siy tap timey ar ak kirgiy tiŋ nup diy, mindrep giniŋgambun.  
\v 4 Nuk gek mindrep giniŋgambun kun ak; tap timey, gos timey lum ar biy mindiy niŋbay ak kirginiŋgambun.   
\p
\v 5-6 Pen kun giy mindrep giniŋg, Gor nup gosimb niŋbim rek nep niŋmindiy, monmon ma giy, gos niŋrep giy, mindrep ginimimb. Gos nimbip key wip rek ma giy, Krays nup chiŋgiy nep mindenimimb.  
\v 7 Mam ay gok kuyip direp giyiŋg, biynimb yikop gok sek wasemb aynimimb.  
\v 8 Pen Krays nup gosimb niŋbim rek, apiyn ar kun ak giy mey, Gor nup woŋg ak gem, amrep yimb giniŋgamb.  
\v 9 Pen nimb gunap minim aŋgiy tiksipiyn kun biy, ma niŋniŋgambim ak; biynimb windin koy gok mey, kun giniŋgambim. Biynimb kun gok rek, Gor kuyip tap siy tap timey geyak, gach wiykyokak ak sakiy giy, nup gosimb niŋnep ma mindpay.   
\p
\v 10 Pen mam ay tep yand gok. Kun ak rek ma ginimimb. Gor gos nuk key niŋiy nimbip dip ak, kilis giy biynimb nuk mindenimimb. Apiyn rek giy mey, ma apyap pikniŋgambim.  
\v 11 Pen Ñinuk Jiysis Krays chinup aŋgiy kumak ak apiy, nimbip wasiw giyiŋg, di biynimb nuk per kond mindeniŋgamb namb ak ay, kond mindeniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 12-14 Kun ak yand Piyta, nimbip minim kun ak, aŋgyiŋg nep mindeniŋgayn. Biyomb chin Jiysis Krays, yip kumniŋgamban aŋgiy ñin aŋgayak ak, maŋ wip ak mey;  
\v 15 mumbwak sek mindpiyn ñin biy, nimbip minim kun ak, aŋgyiŋg nep mindpiyn. Kun ak sakiy ma ginimimb; niŋyiŋg mindenimimb.   
\p
\v 16 Nimbip Jiysis Krays Biyomb key yimb mindiy winiŋgamb aŋgnuk ak; minim nep ma aŋgnuk. Nind Biyomb kun ak key yimb ayek, windin chin key niŋiy, nimbip aŋgnuk.  
\v 17-18 Ñin kun ak, nuk yip am dum bap mindnukniŋ, Gor melik tep ak ap Ñinuk yip mindakniŋ, yimb nup dand aranyiŋg aŋgak, “Bi biy Ñi mapin tep yand; nup niŋen yip tep yimb gip aŋgak.”   
\p
\v 19 Kun ak bi Gor minim aŋgep minim aŋgyak gok, yesek ma aŋgyak; minim pisnep dep gok nep aŋgyak. Minim aŋgyak kun ak, lam kisyimken daŋgiy ayey, chinup melik yomimb rek ak gip. Melik kun ak, niŋdand amiy, gap poŋglin miñmon yowniŋg gakniŋ arachakip rek ak, lim giniŋgamb gos namb nimbip biyaŋ. Lim gek mey, miñmon pisnep yowip rek ak giniŋgamb.  
\v 20 Pen minim nokom bap niŋrep ginjun. Biynimb gunap Gor minim ak yand nep niŋbiyn; nimb ma niŋbim aŋgiy, aŋgniŋgiy rek ma ayip.  
\v 21 Yenen: bi Gor minim aŋgep gok, Baybol buk minim ak tikniŋg, key niŋyak rek ma tikyak; Gor Kawnan ak kuyip gos ñakniŋ nep tikyak.   
\c 2  
\s1 Bi Gor Minim Aspun Aŋgiy, Minim Yesek Aŋgñimbay Gok  
\p
\v 1 Wosrey bi gunap, Gor minim aspun aŋgiy, biynimb chin Yisrel kuyip minim yesek aŋgñiyiŋgipay. Giyak kun ak rek, biynimb gunap namb nimbip ak mindiy, kunep giniŋgambay ak niŋrep ginimimb. Biyomb kuyip aŋgiy kumak ak nup, Biyomb mer aŋgiy aŋgjiw mindyiŋg, ma niŋniŋgambay won ak Gor gek, yiwur yomb yimb ak diniŋgambay.  
\v 2 Pen biynimb kuŋaynep minim kuyip ak diy, tap siy tap timey giyiŋg, biynimb Krays nup kisen gipun gok, yimb chinup taw achip achip giniŋgambay.  
\v 3 Maniy tap gok dun aŋgiy, minim yesek yimb gok aŋgniŋgambay. Kun giniŋgambay ak pen, Gor nuk niŋnep mindip; kor yomb kun ak key niŋniŋgambay.  
\v 4 Gor enjol tap siy tap timey giyak gok kuyip ma kirgak; miñ kilis timey ak ay, kaw miŋgan kisyim wip biyaŋ yokek, kor ak kond mindpay.  
\v 5 Pen biynimb nup alemb alemb ñiyak gok simb ma niŋiy, gek miñmon yomb ak pikiy ñiŋg tan aranek, maŋgiysek ñiŋg ñimbiy kumdiyak. Nowa sek, biynimb nuk onep ar ak sek kuyip nep kond mindek, kim amniyak.  
\v 6 Pen biynimb yip kirginiŋgambay gok, kuyip giniŋgamb rek, maŋgiysek niŋrep giyaŋ aŋgiy, mon maŋlaŋ ak semb biyoŋ nimb yokek apiy, Sodom Gomora biynimb kuyip, pisnep yin simbok amnak.  
\v 7-8 Pen binak Lot nup sek ma yinak; Gor nup kond mindiy, dand mis okok amnak. Nuk bi tep namb kiyk okok mindiy, minek minek timey giyak ak niŋek, yiruk yimb giyiŋgip.  
\v 9 Kun ak chin niŋbun: tap bap Gor biynimb tep nuk gok kuyip giniŋg gek, nuk kuyip kond mindeniŋgamb. Pen biynimb nup kirpay gok aŋgayek, miker diyiŋg, kor yomb ak kond mindeniŋgambay.  
\v 10 Kor yomb kun ak, biynimb minim ma niŋiy, gos kiyk key wip rek gipay gok kuyip aŋgak.  
\p Gor minim aspun aŋgiy, yesek apay kun gok, jel ma gek, enjol tep semb biyoŋ gok kuyip, monmon aŋgjiwpay.  
\v 11 Enjol gok pen, kun ak rek ma gipay. Kiyk biyomb rek mindpay ak pen, bi minim yesek aŋgep kun gok, yerer gipay minim ak, Gor nup aŋgñiniŋg, kuyip aŋgjiwyiŋg yimb kuyip ma taw achip achip gipay.  
\v 12 Pen bi Gor minim aspun aŋgiy, nimbip minim yesek aŋgñimbay kun gok, kanj kimin tap yikop gok, gos ma niŋiy monmon gipay rek ak gipay. Gipay kun ak, kanj kimin gon ayey dip rek ak, kuyip giniŋgamb.  
\v 13 Timey giyiŋg, pumbnamb tap yomb ñimbyiŋg, ñiŋg kilis ñimbyiŋg monmon gi dand amiy, nambiŋ ma dipay ak; pen yiwur diniŋgambay. Pen nimb Gor nup wasemb ayiŋg ap nan-giy, biret wayn ñimbim ñin gok, ap nimb yip wilikpay ak, tep ma gip.  
\v 14 Tap gok chin nep mindeŋ aŋgiy gos anep ayek, biyn siy dun aŋgiy, windin ay nep tapay. Biynimb Krays nup chiŋgrep ma gipay gok kuyip, nembnemb gi dand kind kiyk ak amey, tap siy tap timey gipay. Bi yesek apay kun gok, Gor kuyip yiwur yomb yimb ak ñiniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 15 Kiyk kinjeŋ tep ar ak kirgiy, bi Beyow ñinuk Balam maniy tap gok diyn aŋgiy, Gor minim ak yesek aŋgniŋg gek rek ak gipay.  
\v 16 Kanj doŋgiy gok, minim ma apay ak pen, doŋgiy nuk ak nup bi apay rek aŋg gek, yesek aŋgniŋg gek kun ak kirgak.   
\p
\v 17 Pen minek gunap, ñiŋg malniŋg amiy niŋbun: ñiŋg kilam jiwip gok milip gip. Minek gunap miñmon pikniŋg gek, yiŋgen yomb apiy liŋgek, ma pikip. Kun ak rek mey; Gor minim aŋgñispun aŋgiy, pen yesek nep apay gok. Kun gipay ak, Gor kuyip aŋg kisyim wip namb okok yokniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 18 Bi kun gok, yimb kiyk key dand aranyiŋg apay, “Chinup kisen gem, mindmaŋgiy tikjakniŋgamb rek monmon giniŋgambim apay.” Kun aŋgey mey, biynimb buŋgiy kiyk gok yip monmon gi dand amiy, kisen nep mindrep gipay gok gos ñey, tip ak tap siy tap timey gipay.  
\v 19 Gipay ar kun ak, kalambis woŋg kiyk rek ayip ak kirgiy, yikop mindeniŋgiy rek ma ayip. Pen biynimb kuyip minim aŋgñimbay gok kunep, kalambis woŋg kun ak rek gey amek, yikop mindeniŋgiy rek ma ayip.  
\v 20 Nind Jiysis Krays nup gosimb niŋiy, biynimb yip taŋgiy monmon giyiŋgipay gok, kirgiy mindrep giyak ak pen; tip ak gey amek, yikop mindeniŋgiy rek ma ayip.  
\v 21 Suŋ-tep mindeniŋgiy miñ ak ma niŋbiyap ak, tep rek gipkop. Pen Gor chinup aŋgak ak niŋiy kirpay ak, tep ma yimb giniŋgamb.  
\v 22 Kiyk minim omiŋal wosrey aŋgyiŋgipay ak rek gipay. Minim omiŋal kun ak aŋgyak: “Kayn gok wokay andkind apiy, tap wok aypay ak tip ñimbay.” “Kanj gok ñiŋg pikiy, andkind amiy, tip ak wilemb kolkol gipay aŋgyak.”   
\c 3  
\s1 Biyomb Ak Niŋind Aŋgip Kasek Winiŋgamb  
\p
\v 1 Biynimb tep yand gok. Nimbip minj bap nind tikyokiy, miñiy bap tiksipiyn ak; minim kun ak tip aŋgen niŋrep giy, gos tep yimb ak niŋnimimb aŋgiy tiksipiyn.  
\v 2 Bi Gor minim aŋgep suŋ-tep gok sek, bi Jiysis minim dand amemb nimb gok sek minim aŋgñiyak rek, niŋmindenimimb apiyn.   
\p
\v 3 Pen niŋim: ñin kisen mindpun biy rek, biynimb minim tep ak aŋgjiwiy, gos key niŋbay rek giy mindrep ma gipay gunap, nimbip aŋgniŋgambay,  
\v 4 “Bi winiŋgayn aŋgiy aŋgayak ak, winiŋgamb miŋgan akay nimb? Biynimb nindik gok mindyakniŋ, winiŋgayn aŋgak ak pen; kiyk kumdipay ak ma wip. Alwol gayak ñin ak, mindek rek nep mindip aŋgniŋgambay.”  
\v 5 Bi kun gok, Gor miñmon gay kond mindip ak, niŋrep gipay ak pen; ñinen kirpay. Pen nuk nep aŋgek, semb biyoŋ ay, ñiŋg ak kus kus giy, man ak namb biyaŋ ay gak.  
\v 6 Kisen aŋgek, ñiŋg ap mankumb biy yiwgek, pisnep timey gak.  
\v 7 Pen nuk nep aŋgek, semb biyoŋ, man biy mindrep gisap. Biynimb nup kirpay gok kuyip, kor giy yiwur yomb ñiniŋgayn ñin ak, pisnep daŋgiyen yiniŋgamb aŋgiy niŋmindip.   
\p
\v 8 Pen biynimb tep yand yimb gok. Minim bap sakiy ginimimb rek ayip. Chin simiy kuŋay yimb nep ñin paŋg niŋbun ak pen, Gor niŋek, ñin nokom bap rek ayip.  
\v 9 Kun ak nuk winiŋgayn aŋgiy kasek ma wip ak, biynimb gunap minim nep aŋgiy kirpay rek ma gip; biynimb tap siy tap timey giy, mon key yinjap amniŋg gispay gok, gunap ma kurginiŋgiy, yip ker apey, kuyip diyn aŋgiy, kond mindip.   
\p
\v 10 Pen Biyomb winiŋgamb ak; bi tap siy dep gok, niŋmindey ma opay rek ak winiŋgamb. Ñin kun ak, giw parsek aŋgakniŋ, semb muk biyoŋ keykey amniŋgamb. Gap tap yerip yerip semb biyoŋ mindip gok yiniy, man biy tap yerip yerip mindip gok maŋgiysek yiniŋgamb.   
\p
\v 11 Maŋgiysek yiniŋgamb kun ak rek, mindrep ginjun akaŋ monmon ginjun? Ñin yomb winiŋg gisap kun ak niŋiy, Gor aŋgip rek giy mindrep ginjun.  
\v 12 Pen minim tep nup ak, biynimb okok kuyip aŋgyiŋg mindon, ñin yomb nuk ak kasek winimuŋ. Ñin kun ak, takin, gap, tap semb biyoŋ gok, yin ñiŋgband tikniŋgamb ak pen;  
\v 13 Gor semb biyoŋ sek, man biy sek kisenimb giniŋgayn aŋgiy, minim aŋgayak ak kond mindpun. Namb kun ak, tap siy tap timey bap ma giy; nuk yip mindiy, mindrep yimb giniŋgambun.   
\p
\v 14 Kun ak biynimb tep yand gok. Nuk asaw aŋgiy kond mindpim ñin biy, jimñiy mindiy, biynimb suŋ-tep minim ma mindip gok mindonjun aŋgiy gem amek mey, ap nimbip niŋek tep yimb ginimuŋ.  
\v 15 Pen nuk kasek ma wip ak; biynimb gunap sek yip ker wiyaŋ aŋgiy, kond mindip. Gor mam tep chin Pol nup gos tep ñakniŋ, nimbip minj tikiy, minim nokom kun ak rek aŋgak.  
\v 16 Minj nuk tikak gok, minim kosyam niŋep rek gunap sek aŋgek mey; biynimb mindrep ma gipay gok niŋiy, minim kun ak tuŋgandikiy, minim yesek ar ak apay. Pol nup minim ak nep kun ma gipay; Gor minim bi gunap tikyak ak kunep gipay. Gipay kun ak, kinjeŋ kiyk bap ma mindip.   
\p
\v 17 Pen biynimb tep yand gok. Gos niŋbim kun ak, niŋrep ginimimb. Mer ak, kiyk gos timey niŋiy, timey gipay rek giy, apyap pikniŋgambim.  
\v 18 Pen Biyomb chin Jiysis Krays biynimb simb niŋiy, di Nop yip jimñiy ayip ak nup niŋbim rek; nup niŋrep yimb giy, mindrep yimb ginjun aŋgiy mindenimimb. Bi tep chin kun ak, yimb nup ak pernep dand araniŋgiy! Tep.   